title: Ep 38: Why Do We Sabotage Ourselves?
description: In this episode, Pat Keane and I discuss self sabotage and motivation. Why do we fail ourselves at crucial moments? What is the payoff? Who knows more sports analogies than Pat Keane?
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
